instructions: ping - The latency for the bot. The API latency is the bot and the server.
play <newActivity> - Sets a new activity to play.
say <text> - Makes the bot send a message.
kick <member> <reason> - Allows administrators to kick memebers.
ban <member> <reason> - Allows administrators to ban memebers.
purge <number> - Allows for bulk deletion of messages from all users up to 100.
prefix <newPrefix> - Sets the prefix to whatever the user wants.
